long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Rapid and Private AI chat assistant Plugin

You can use it directly from the sidebar by clicking the plugin icon.

If the plugin does not activate when you click the icon, you can manually enable it as follows:
1. Click the sidebar button in the menu bar (next to the avatar).
2. In the panel that opens, click the dropdown menu in the top left corner and select “Jack’s ChatGPT.”

Official website: https://chat-two.emmmm.dev?source=extension_store
long.zh_CN,zh_TW:
快速且隐私安全的 ChatGPT 插件
---
您可以直接在侧边栏中使用，点击插件图标即可。

---
如果点击插件图标未开启，可手动开启，方法如下：
1. 点击菜单栏的侧边栏按钮（在头像旁边）
2. 在打开的面板中，点击左上角的下拉菜单，选择“Jack's ChatGPT” 即可

官网地址：https://chat-two.emmmm.dev?source=extension_store
